Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:32.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}昨日までとなにか違う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:38.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな涙も光に変わるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:44.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}きっと二人が出逢えた秘密がある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on me　きらりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on you　突然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:52.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なんだっていまから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}できちゃいそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:57.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on me　かならず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:00.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on you　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:02.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ほんとうの未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:05.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そばにあること
