Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:44.59,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(349,620)\be2}「捉對廝殺」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開局應該是相同位置的一對一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打破均勢之前  先集中精神對付眼前對手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方擁有著突破能力很高的前衛和中衛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開局我們就加強防守  阻止對方前進的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位就精神抖擻地開始比賽吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Wing Road
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架空段道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Air Liner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃空航道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒跟埃裏奧進行一對一較量了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意的話沒準會被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(691,646)\fs36}Strada
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  拓路雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要擊落菲特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.74,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)\bord1.5\fs40}Ja boul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.74,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)\bord1.5}瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了  莉奧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  薇薇歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜同學  就拜託你做莉奧同學的對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(492,646)\fs36}fullback
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  作為後衛  誰能支援好自己的隊伍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被奈葉的大招擊中  會有瞬間全滅的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞娜的穿甲狙擊彈比我的要更快更硬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她得逞的話我和隊友都會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必勝的一擊就在——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破數量均勢的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然厲害  諾威
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此  我也是你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Caliber Shot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛輪衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不論工作如何  若論格鬥技…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Revolver Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴旋釘刺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格鬥技還不能與愛因哈特匹敵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果能使用魔法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一閃必中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Divine Buster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖光衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高速炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能擦到也算非常成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來才是重頭戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐的魔法也很直率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種半吊子射炮擊對霸王流是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是準備動作？  愛因哈特也會中距離攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  對射正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐遊戲玩完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不太擅長跑跳  就在這對戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜的魔法也具有個性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處於被動的話就不好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她停下來了  那就先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了  珂羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙龍圓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我格鬥技和魔法戰都不是非常擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍有一項
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前被薇薇歐誇獎過的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心得一直在訓練的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Creation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創成啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(293,646)\fs36}水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以魔導器為核心注入魔力  自由操控淬煉出的物質
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(754,646)\fs36}Golem Create
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的  魔像創成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(806,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以創主珂羅娜和魔導器布倫希爾之名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(714,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊碎她  歌利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中衛們在互相牽制著  陣型也很完整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是場很明快的戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(471,646)\fs36}fullback
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位後衛也快完成支援的設置了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前衛們的平衡也會開始被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Sonic Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音速射手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  愛因哈特處於守勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在命中的同時迂迴過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被接住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不破壞彈殼的情況下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王流  旋衝破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個好厲害  是炮彈反射？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是反射也不是吸收放射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是「接住了再扔回去」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情能做到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上  古代貝魯卡的術者是能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但話說回來  小小年紀就有那種技術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她究竟經歷了多麼苛刻的修煉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐的反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打偏一點結果可能就反過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種時機使出那種反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐同學果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特  停手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的損傷能讓薇薇歐暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此機會率先突破進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進藍隊的中衛  奈葉小姐那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害  居然有那種招式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐受到激勵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只剩三位數的生命值  放她去追擊恐怕不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐  暫且回來接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛開局就折損掉兩路前衛之一不太好吧  快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在魔像上用這招好像有點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:28.84,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)\bord1.5\fs40}I also think so
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:28.84,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)\bord1.5}我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  珂羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種快速的魔像操作不是一般人能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.19,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)\bord1.5\fs40}Her damage is less than the expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.19,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)\bord1.5}她受的損傷比預計的小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉奧也很擅長防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定進行了非常多的研究和練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要比私下的練習量和求勝心的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷神裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟雷炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.98,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,625)\bord1.5\fs40}Your friend is very powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.98,POS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)\bord1.5}主人的朋友力氣真大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,646)\fs36}Brunzell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布倫希爾  別說的這麼悠閒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉奧好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露·露  快點恢復啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急別急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等完全恢復了之後再出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我們隊的前中衛可沒有那麼簡單被打敗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃裏奧真的變強了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始我就已經全力攻擊了  但卻沒法直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃裏奧  這裏是露提希亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐的恢復還需要些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  麻煩你拖住菲特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍隊隊員們  等薇薇歐恢復之後就開始進行那個作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請做好隨時行動的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞小姐  小露好像有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子打起鬼主意來可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特  對方的作戰核心毫無疑問是奈葉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力阻止奈葉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐同學的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不嫌棄  樂意奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍隊中衛  高町奈葉向各隊員報告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將與紅隊前衛愛因哈特接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊支援將會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意迪亞娜和琦蘿的支援攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,646)\fs36}Accel Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速射手  彈幕集中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Photon Smasher
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子轟擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？  厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小霸王在壓制著奈葉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在承受攻擊的同時她也在分析呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種態勢  奈葉好像很享受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然動作還很粗糙  不過基本功很扎實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定做了相當大量的基礎訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像被看穿一樣一一防住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只要這樣繼續攻擊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特  小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過於傾向攻擊的話  奈葉小姐的那個就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是敵隊的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破防了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右拳擺拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,646)\fs36}Banding Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束縛盾  捕獲確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了  這是奈葉小姐封鎖近身的必勝模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊？躲不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣  想起你學會的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(619,646)\fs36}Excellion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強化…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從放鬆的靜止狀態開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由腳尖帶動下半身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身帶動上半身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借由旋轉的加速將拳頭推出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Strike Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強襲星爆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被完全吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真正的炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在那之前我所打出的一擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用打擊的威力掙脫了束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這炮彈是…  迪亞娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特  幹的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福  裝填和佈置全都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是紅隊勝利的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,646)\fs36}Crossfire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(735,646)\fs36}Full Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交叉炮火  極限火力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自遠方來到近前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓年輕的碧眼霸王來到我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是召喚魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給你治療  一會還要麻煩你回前線哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Boosted Healing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極速治療
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母  剛才小霸王做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要精通調整加速和爆發點的打擊方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以發揮出各種不同的效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特所做的就是從靜止狀態開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用全身的加速使威力爆發的打擊方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發揮到極致的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護盾和束縛在愛因哈特面前都將變得毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她習得了無法束縛之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Unchain Knuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏈破碎拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你教會愛因哈特啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(397,646)\fs36}Unchain Knuckle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏈破碎拳  那是我們媽媽的拿手絕技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只教了她水斬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的都是靠她自己領悟的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來諾威
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下和我的一對一  你打算去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去攻擊後衛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去還可以把大小姐和虛弱的薇薇歐一網打盡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追的上的話就來追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  諾威攻過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露·露  治療到這個程度就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  愛因哈特也在進行治療
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(618,646)\fs36}Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜的歌利亞還沒爬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是個好機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍隊的各位  雖然比預定計劃有些提前  開始作戰計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二對一？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露  竟敢無視我和珂羅娜  膽子不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是膽量  而是智慧的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前中衛是配合默契的好搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以快攻將對手各個擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我和莉奧從中距離封殺琦蘿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是藍隊的必勝策略
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特  我用防護罩保護你  你先在這裏等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅隊隊員是不會被輕易打敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  珂羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅隊陷入危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞娜和珂羅娜要去支援才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞娜似乎有不同的想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始已經12分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥空域的魔力散佈已經非常充分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數均勢已經被打破  現在對方站位非常集中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是發射逆轉一擊的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞娜消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算挑個位置發射炮擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍隊各隊員  作戰通告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行防禦戰的同時盡可能將戰鬥區域向中央集中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用集束炮一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到一絲恐怖的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這場混戰會出乎意料地迅速決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這樣待在後方  我更想站在前線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的一擊  我的霸王流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想進一步地確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:40.97,NETITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\pos(640,720)\1cBF6E0A}「新的舞台」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goliath
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也想站上去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  等到結束之後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Magical
